          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors. The production yields from some previously",
                "well-known systems at the addition of C-F(4) was",
                "present. Successful tests have been done with a target",
                "of Nb foil combined with a W-surface ionizer, with a",
                "target of Ta foil with a hot plasma-discharge ion-",
                "source, with a target of molten La with a W-surface",
                "ionizer, and with a Ti foil target combined with a W-",
                "surface ionizer. In all cases, the C-F(4) strongly",
                "improved the conditions for a number of elements."
              ]
            }
          ],
